dct_title_s: Reconnaissance map of the Fairbanks quadrangle, Alaska
dct_description_sm: Alfred H. Brooks, Geologist in charge ; Surveyed in 1903, 1905, 1906, 1907, and 1908.
Relief shown by contours, spot heights, and form lines for unsurveyed areas.
